# Cloudflare Pages redirects for the freeCodeCamp UIKit docs site.
#
# Format: `[source] [destination] [code?]` (one per line).
# Spec:   https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
# Limits: 2,000 static + 100 dynamic per file (well within scope).
#
# This file is intentionally empty at first deploy - the docs site has no
# legacy URLs to redirect from, and Astro emits canonical trailing-slash
# directories for every page.
#
# Future entries should appear with: static rules first, dynamic rules
# (with splats / placeholders) last. Order matters: the top-most match wins.
